---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="AI Copyright Law by Country — Global Legal Guide"
  description="Compare AI copyright laws across the US, EU, UK, Japan, and more. Understand how different jurisdictions handle AI-generated content and training data."
>
  <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <div class="mb-10">
      <h1 class="font-heading text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-text mb-3">AI Copyright Laws by Country</h1>
      <p class="text-text-muted text-lg">How different jurisdictions handle AI-generated content, training data, and creator rights.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <a href="/laws/united-states" class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-slate-200 p-6 hover:shadow-lg transition-all group">
        <div class="text-3xl mb-3">🇺🇸</div>
        <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-lg text-text group-hover:text-primary transition-colors mb-2">United States</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-muted">Human authorship required. Fair use debates ongoing. Most active litigation globally.</p>
        <span class="inline-block mt-3 px-2 py-0.5 bg-green-50 text-green-700 text-xs font-semibold rounded">Most Developed</span>
      </a>

      <a href="/laws/european-union" class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-slate-200 p-6 hover:shadow-lg transition-all group">
        <div class="text-3xl mb-3">🇪🇺</div>
        <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-lg text-text group-hover:text-primary transition-colors mb-2">European Union</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-muted">EU AI Act in force. Text & data mining exceptions with opt-out rights for creators.</p>
        <span class="inline-block mt-3 px-2 py-0.5 bg-blue-50 text-blue-700 text-xs font-semibold rounded">AI Act Active</span>
      </a>

      <a href="/laws/united-kingdom" class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-slate-200 p-6 hover:shadow-lg transition-all group">
        <div class="text-3xl mb-3">🇬🇧</div>
        <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-lg text-text group-hover:text-primary transition-colors mb-2">United Kingdom</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-muted">Computer-generated works provision (s.9(3) CDPA 1988). Code of Practice in development.</p>
        <span class="inline-block mt-3 px-2 py-0.5 bg-amber-50 text-amber-700 text-xs font-semibold rounded">Evolving</span>
      </a>

      <a href="/laws/japan" class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-slate-200 p-6 hover:shadow-lg transition-all group">
        <div class="text-3xl mb-3">🇯🇵</div>
        <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-lg text-text group-hover:text-primary transition-colors mb-2">Japan</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-muted">Broad exception for AI training under Article 30-4. Most permissive major jurisdiction.</p>
        <span class="inline-block mt-3 px-2 py-0.5 bg-purple-50 text-purple-700 text-xs font-semibold rounded">AI-Friendly</span>
      </a>

      <a href="/laws/china" class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-slate-200 p-6 hover:shadow-lg transition-all group">
        <div class="text-3xl mb-3">🇨🇳</div>
        <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-lg text-text group-hover:text-primary transition-colors mb-2">China</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-muted">Beijing Internet Court recognized AI image copyright (Nov 2023). Rapidly developing framework.</p>
        <span class="inline-block mt-3 px-2 py-0.5 bg-red-50 text-red-700 text-xs font-semibold rounded">Emerging</span>
      </a>

      <a href="/laws/indonesia" class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-slate-200 p-6 hover:shadow-lg transition-all group">
        <div class="text-3xl mb-3">🇮🇩</div>
        <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-lg text-text group-hover:text-primary transition-colors mb-2">Indonesia</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-muted">Copyright Law No. 28/2014 requires human authorship. No specific AI provisions yet.</p>
        <span class="inline-block mt-3 px-2 py-0.5 bg-slate-100 text-slate-600 text-xs font-semibold rounded">No AI-Specific Law</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
